<paragraph blockId="1.[835,1474,924,1377]" pageId="1" pageNumber="147">
<keyLead pageId="1" pageNumber="147">– Mesonotum and tergites shining metallic green. Medium-sized species (4.5–7.3 mm) with apical aristal segment shorter or about half as long as apical aristal segment ....................... 2</keyLead>
