<figureCitation box="[1192,1286,1154,1175]" captionStart="Figs" captionStartId="3.[136,180,2063,2084]" captionTargetBox="[310,1327,1211,2039]" captionTargetId="figure-7@3.[265,1347,1192,2050]" captionTargetPageId="3" captionText="Figs. 4–5. Ngirhaphium murphyi, Evenhuis &amp; Grootaert: 4, Dorsal view of genital capsule; 5, Lateral view of genital capsule with left ventral surstylus removed, hypandrium at the front, right ventral surstylus at the back." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4502154" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/4502154/files/figure.png" pageId="1" pageNumber="147">Figs. 4, 5</figureCitation>
